>Auto-translate: Ga</option><option value="Hausa">Auto-translate: Hausa</option><option value="Dagbani">Auto-translate: Dagbani</option></select></div><div class="qcard"><div class="qmeta"><span class="chip cg" id="q-sub-chip">Math</span><span style="font-size:12px;color:var(--muted);" id="q-diff-lbl">Beginner</span><span style="font-size:12px;color:var(--muted);margin-left:auto;" id="q-num-lbl">Q1</span><div class="timer-ring" id="t-ring"><svg width="44" height="44" viewBox="0 0 44 44"><circle class="tr-bg" cx="22" cy="22" r="18" stroke-dasharray="113" stroke-dashoffset="0"/><circle class="tr-fg" id="t-circle" cx="22" cy="22" r="18" stroke-dasharray="113" stroke-dashoffset="0"/></svg><div class="tr-num" id="t-num">30</div></div></div><div class="pbar-bg"><div class="pbar-fill" id="q-pbar" style="width:2%;"></div></div><div id="q-question"><div class="lr"><div class="sp"></div>Generating question...</div></div><div id="q-options"></div><div id="q-written" style="display:none;"><textarea id="q-written-input" placeholder="Type your answer here..."></textarea><button class="btn bp bsm" style="margin-top:8px;" onclick="submitWritten()" id="q-sub-written">Submit Answer</button></div><div id="q-hint"></div><div id="q-feedback"></div><div id="q-trans"></div><div class="arow"><button class="btn bs bsm" id="q-hint-btn" onclick="showHint()">💡 Hint</button><button class="btn bp" id="q-next-btn" onclick="nextQ()" style="display:none;min-width:110px;">Next →</button><button class="btn bs bsm" onclick="skipQ()">Skip</button><button class="btn bsm bgr" id="q-trans-btn" onclick="translateAns()" style="display:none;">🌍 Translate</button>
