<div id="pg-tutor" class="page"><div class="tnav"><button class="back-btn" onclick="goPage('home')">←</button><div class="page-title">AI Tutor</div><select id="tutor-lang" style="font-size:12px;padding:5px 8px;border-radius:8px;background:var(--bg2);border:1px solid var(--border2);color:var(--text);font-family:var(--fb);width:auto;"><option value="English">English</option><option value="Twi">Twi</option><option value="Fante">Fante</option><option value="Ewe">Ewe</option><option value="Ga">Ga</option><option value="Hausa">Hausa</option><option value="Dagbani">Dagbani</option></select></div><div class="page-body"><div class="wrap"><div class="chat-win" id="chat-win"><div class="msg-ai"><div class="ai-label">Nyansa AI Tutor</div>Akwaaba! 👋 I am your personal AI tutor for all GES subjects — Basic to SHS.<br><br>Type a question like <strong>&ldquo;Explain quadratic equations&rdquo;</strong> or <strong>&ldquo;Help me write a WASSCE essay.&rdquo;</strong><br><br>💡 <em>Tip: Type a subject name like &ldquo;Physics&rdquo; and I will show topics to pick from!</em><br><br>I can explain in English, Twi, Fante, Ewe, Ga, Hausa, or Dagbani!</div></div><div class="chat-row"><input type="text" id="chat-input" placeholder="e.g. Explain photosynthesis in Twi..." onkeydown="if(event.key==='Enter')sendChat()"><button class="btn bp bsm" id="chat-send" onclick="sendChat()">Send ↗</button></div><div class="qa-row"><button class="qa-btn" onclick="quickAsk('Explain quadratic equations step by step')">📐 Quadratics</button><button class="qa-btn" onclick="quickAsk('Explain the water cycle with Ghana examples')">🌧️ Water Cycle</button><button class="qa-btn" onclick="quickAsk('How do I write a good WASSCE essay?')">✍️ Essay writing</button><button class="qa-btn" onclick="quickAsk('Explain supply and demand using Ghana market examples')">📈 Economics</button><button class="qa-btn" onclick="quickAsk('Explain the causes of the 1966 coup in Ghana')">🇬🇭 Ghana history</button><button class="qa-btn" onclick="quickAsk('What is the difference between acids and bases?')">🧪 Chemistry</button><button class="qa-btn" onclick="quickAsk('Explain Ohms Law with a worked example')">⚡ Physics</button><button class="qa-btn" onclick="quickAsk('Help me understand the 1992 Constitution of Ghana')">⚖️ Government</button><button class="qa-btn" style="background:rgba(0,107,63,.07);border-color:rgba(0,107,63,.2);color:#006b3f;" onclick="quickAsk('Explain photosynthesis in Twi language')">🇬🇭 In Twi</button></div></div></div><div class="bnav"><button class="bni" onclick="goPage('home')"><div class="bni-ico">🏠</div><div class="bni-lbl">Home</div></button><button class="bni" onclick="goPage('quiz')"><div class="bni-ico">🎯</div><div class="bni-lbl">Quiz</div></button><button class="bni active" onclick="goPage('tutor')"><div class="bni-ico">🤖</div><div class="bni-lbl">AI Tutor</div></button><button class="bni" onclick="goPage('history')"><div class="bni-ico">📊</div><div class="bni-lbl">History</div></button><button class="bni" onclick="goPage('settings')"><div class="bni-ico">⚙️</div><div class="bni-lbl">Settings</div></button></div>
